USB Connectors
--------------

There are 2 x Type A **USB HOST connectors** onboard, as shown on *Figure 4*.

.. Figure:: /Media/ARM/A8/AM3354/USB_OTG.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center
  
  *Figure 4: USB HOST Connectors (embedded/enclosed PC version)*

.. note::
  The OTG Connector is defined as HOST by default. If customer needs it work as OTG (slave), please remove 0â„¦ Resistor R119 and R121 as shown in Figure 4.
  
.. warning::
 
  Be careful not to touch surrounding electronic components accidentally while plugging in USB devices into the embedded Industrial PC version.